INSERT INTO beliefs VALUES('88e3fd78-8b3a-4a3c-aba1-90d029a6c83e','Display server (server.mjs) needed SPA fallback: when a file under /apps/<name>/ is not found and has no extension, serve index.html instead of 404. Fixed 2026-03-18. Root cause: React Router client-side routes like /admin were hitting the static file server which returned 404.','pattern','fact',0.949999999999999955,5,'["display-server","spa-routing","fix"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1773873344176,1773873344176,NULL,1775151906532,'Contradicted by 62dcf304 (auto-resolved by curate)',1773873344);
INSERT INTO beliefs VALUES('62dcf304-6736-4558-96d0-7e9c3ab62ed3','yeli-moov comprehensive e2e test completed 2026-03-19. 10 bugs found and fixed: NotificationContext crash, login token mismatch, lead search not implemented, commission stats wrong key, NewConversationModal wrong key, conversations showing Inconnu, message thread empty, messages button invisible in dark mode, dark mode class not applied to HTML, login page white background leak. 8/8 pages pass, all CRUD verified, zero JS errors. Dark mode fully working (43+ files). Final build deployed.','project','fact',0.192670037499999668,5,'["yeli-moov","e2e-test","bugs-fixed"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1773880756303,1775383238564,NULL,1775383238658,'Confidence below threshold (< 0.2)',1773880756);
INSERT INTO beliefs VALUES('033acb03-73c6-43a5-b050-920a1f9f93fa','wa send CLI fails with ''invalid json'' on multiline messages or messages with special characters. Root cause: the CLI passes the message as a shell argument which breaks JSON serialization when it contains newlines or quotes. Workaround: use Python urllib to POST directly to http://127.0.0.1:7777/send with proper JSON encoding. This has failed 3+ times. Need to fix the CLI or build a wrapper.','pattern','fact',0.949999999999999955,5,'["wa-cli","bug","multiline","fix-needed"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1773881269969,1773881269969,NULL,1774438529,'Superseded by belief 1aefd4cf which confirms wa send multiline bug FIXED on 2026-03-19. The bug described here was resolved.',1773881269);
INSERT INTO beliefs VALUES('1aefd4cf-763d-4988-bf8f-236af1a77018','wa send multiline bug FIXED on 2026-03-19. Root cause: raw string interpolation in curl JSON payload. Fix: use python3 json.dumps for proper encoding. Commit f479404 in ccrice.','pattern','fact',0.949999999999999955,5,'["wa-cli","fix-applied"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1773881319534,1773881319534,NULL,1775151906546,'Contradicted by fdc56aa2 (auto-resolved by curate)',1773881319);
INSERT INTO beliefs VALUES('fdc56aa2-f580-49a4-88e0-e1ae2cd6bb77','fang-poll false positive bug FIXED on 2026-03-19. Root cause: 1) fmt.mjs only included ID column when hasMedia=true, so text-only chats had no ID column. 2) fang-poll parsed formatted table output, grabbing Content as the watermark ID. 3) tr -d [:space:] in watermark read stripped spaces within IDs. Fix: rewrote fang-poll to use raw JSON API via python3 instead of parsing formatted table output. Also fixed fmt.mjs to always include ID column.','pattern','fact',0.949999999999999955,5,'["fang-poll","watermark","fix-applied"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1773895493885,1773895493885,NULL,1775151906548,'Contradicted by 786ff3bc (auto-resolved by curate)',1773895493);
